      "title": "Williamsburg Brooklyn Tattoo Studios | Atelier Eva",
      "sourceText": [
        [
          "The entire process of getting a tattoo here was as easy and seamless as possible.",
          "They were very prompt, responsive and helpful after receiving my inquiry.",
          "The studio itself is beautiful; the reviews saying it feels like a spa are completely accurate.",
          "You feel at ease from the moment you step in.",
          "My tattoo artist was Justin and he was incredibly patient in creating my design, made multiple drafts/edits, and made me feel totally comfortable.",
          "They are moderately pricey but it is worth it, you are paying for excellent quality and customer service.",
          "I would 100% come back here!",
          "— Maria (5 Star Review Google My Business ) I went to Atelier Eva for my first tattoo ever, and I had an incredible experience.",
          "The staff were very kind and took all of the proper precautions for COVID-19.",
          "The studio space was beautiful and calming; they are very dedicated to giving the customer the best experience possible.",
          "My tattoo came out more beautifully than I had ever imagined; I will definitely be coming back in the future.",
          "Highly recommend Atelier Eva for your next tattoo!",
          "— Jacqueline (5 Star Review Yelp ) I have been wanting to go to Eva for a long time… even before she opened her own studio.",
          "I love her work, and having met her she’s quite professional and has a tender touch.",
          "I hope I can get something else done by her one day but I’ve gotta save my pennies lol.",
          "But excellent art ain’t cheap.",
          "I go for quality over quantity.",
          "Experienced tattoo artists."
        ]
      ],
